{"id": "1282699834565853215", "channel_id": "1282699834565853215", "type": 0, "author_id": "1278437147896057886", "author_name": "ioshift_24740", "author_bot": false, "content": "技能描述上【打击】和【防御】是加临时力量，但试用里的实际效果好像是永久的？\n配图是试用里面只打出一张【防御】的效果截图", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T13:51:11.971000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1282699835174031481", "filename": "20240909214853.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2239947, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1282699834565853215/1282699835174031481/20240909214853.png?ex=6a008d50&is=69ff3bd0&hm=9870b2caedb40860a8c6df32e7ef03e6daf53f684b6e8032468eba9d82d744cb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282699834565853215", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈姆林技能描述有误？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1282575480083709983", "channel_id": "1282575480083709983", "type": 0, "author_id": "1226317601831911467", "author_name": "tranquil_monkey_73179", "author_bot": false, "content": "一下子7个礼包砸我头上要求我在3天之内全部氪完？？？？？\n所以就是这么逼氪老玩家的吗？\n本来还想氪个大月卡的，现在搞得我连大月卡都不想买了。", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T05:37:03.552000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1282575480821649430", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-09-09-13-32-20-86_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 82530, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1282575480083709983/1282575480821649430/Screenshot_2024-09-09-13-32-20-86_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=6a00c23f&is=69ff70bf&hm=bb467a6e2499cd6f034a29598f8b00f6790791e5e7ac9a0faa81b7d1ba2e0ba2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282575480083709983", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "建议取消主线礼包的时间限制", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1282723810323468298", "channel_id": "1282723810323468298", "type": 0, "author_id": "501758744175181825", "author_name": "inukami2266", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題，池太少了\n禮包一直賣，先不討論觀感好不好看、吃象好不好看\n石頭根本沒有地方消化，對營收也沒有幫助\n\n建議一個界域開一池 渾沌/血肉/深海/超維 各1\n\n然後各限定輪迴，各錯開一星期換角色也行\n算了一下現在各界域應該都有3限定以上了吧\n不論新/老手想玩什麼類型都可以試著捕啟靈or抽來玩看看\n尤其現在STEAM剛上不久，新玩家更多\n\"例如\"現在血肉核心就是羊媽，想要等羊媽池不知遙遙無期\n只想補啟靈又不知道要排幾個界域之後\n至於支線故事開不開無所謂，神父池都卡好幾週了\n想玩其他界域又不想抽一般池\n開了超限爆發系統就算想補命座每隻角色又不知道要等幾個月\n更不用說沉澱商店有更多東西要買\n\n所以這邊建議一個界域各開一池", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T15:26:28.237000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282723810323468298", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "池開太少了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1282782187305046087", "channel_id": "1282782187305046087", "type": 0, "author_id": "685720172451201047", "author_name": "valien_248", "author_bot": false, "content": "是未來會放到主線還是這隻角色直接沒有故事呢？很喜歡所以蠻想看故事的\n\n目前本人在第七章前，不太清楚後面是不是有出現<:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T19:18:26.394000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282782187305046087", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "這次哈姆林活動沒有故事嗎？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1282610672018133045", "channel_id": "1282610672018133045", "type": 0, "author_id": "1222582796816744458", "author_name": "zhaoxing233", "author_bot": false, "content": "安魂曲:裝備者造成傷害時，獲得8%臨時暴擊率\n薔薇:裝備者每造成1次傷害，使裝備者獲得2%臨時暴擊傷害\n安魂曲的臨時暴擊率未加“裝備者獲得”描述，但与薔薇的暴擊傷害一樣是只有裝備者享受", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T07:56:53.963000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😱", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1282610672185643008", "filename": "Image_1725868290511.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 19178, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1282610672018133045/1282610672185643008/Image_1725868290511.jpg?ex=6a003a46&is=69fee8c6&hm=81f128e4275ec2a1843d7f54e784b46bc12cd988a1d645d335e3fae28c60a028&"}, {"id": "1282610672420520008", "filename": "Image_1725868289321.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 21316, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1282610672018133045/1282610672420520008/Image_1725868289321.jpg?ex=6a003a46&is=69fee8c6&hm=78407b677b28c88e713d40c7add6b8d7488f53c8999d88b62153edc16e13696e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282610672018133045", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "命輪安魂曲描述問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1282572359697563648", "channel_id": "1282572359697563648", "type": 0, "author_id": "1195346100677259305", "author_name": "liyh1999", "author_bot": false, "content": "請不要對限時禮包有這麼深的執念🥲🥲，這個跟之前的最開始限時後面又改為常駐的主線禮包沒多少區別吧，對於已經通關之前主線的老玩家有點太措手不及了，無論如何限時3天的時間太短了，請考慮延長可以購買的時間或者乾脆改為常駐<:flop:1236937860922343466> <:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T05:24:39.594000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1282572359932313651", "filename": "IMG_20240909_132336.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 81887, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1282572359697563648/1282572359932313651/IMG_20240909_132336.jpg?ex=6a00bf57&is=69ff6dd7&hm=c9aaa825dd8a156eb0092cb0590ae67688448c18621c04d4d9c228476c77cee7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282572359697563648", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "壞貓TV之主線限時禮包再來", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
